ch will be available in District Level Hospitals including Capital Hospital & RGH, Rourkela as part of commitment to realize [#SusthaOdishaSukhiOdisha](https://twitter.com/hashtag/SusthaOdishaSukhiOdisha?src=hash&ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw). DHHs will be developed with appropriate infra for the programme [pic.twitter.com/S7593orJuy](https://t.co/S7593orJuy)", "005-normal": "\u2014 CMO Odisha (@CMO\\_Odisha) [November 8, 2019](https://twitter.com/CMO_Odisha/status/1192646231803060224?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw)", "006-normal": "", "007-normal": "Induction and refresher training of medical officers and staff nurses and counselors will be taken up regularly to increase proficiency of staff.", "008-normal": "Source / Reference Link: https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/bhubaneswar/district-palliative-care-programme-launched-in-odisha/articleshow/71957333.cms"}}